<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q60_v12" title="Q60_v12" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En un grupo de datos, la desviación de un dato se calcula como 
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi>
      </m:math>, tal que x es el dato y p es el promedio de los datos del grupo.
    </p>
    <p>Considera las masas (en gramos)
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>4,94</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>4,97</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>4,99</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>5,03</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>5,05</m:mn>
      </m:math>, cuyo promedio es 
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>4,996</m:mn>
      </m:math>.
      Observa que tres de las masas son menores que el promedio y dos son mayores.
      Si se calcula la desviación de cada una de estas cinco masas respecto de su promedio, ¿cuál sería la mediana de esas desviaciones?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">-0,001<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Las desviaciones son <m:math><m:mn>4,94</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−0,056</m:mn></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>4,97</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−0,026</m:mn></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>4,99</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>5,03</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,034</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mn>5,05</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,054</m:mn></m:math>. Ordenadas, quedan <m:math><m:mn>−0,056</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>−0,026</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>0,034</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>0,054</m:mn></m:math>. La mediana es el tercer valor, <m:math><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>−0,001</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">-0,006<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Las desviaciones respecto del promedio <m:math><m:mn>4,996</m:mn></m:math> son <m:math><m:mn>−0,056</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>−0,026</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,034</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,054</m:mn></m:math>. Como ya están ordenadas de menor a mayor, la mediana de cinco datos es el tercero, es decir, <m:math><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">0<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Ninguna desviación es <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>, porque ninguna masa es igual al promedio <m:math><m:mn>4,996</m:mn></m:math>. Al calcular, se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>−0,056</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>−0,026</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,034</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,054</m:mn></m:math>. La mediana es el tercer valor, <m:math><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">0,006<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La desviación de <m:math><m:mn>4,99</m:mn></m:math> es <m:math><m:mn>4,99</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>0,006</m:mn></m:math>. Las cinco desviaciones son <m:math><m:mn>−0,056</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>−0,026</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,034</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,054</m:mn></m:math>, y la mediana es el tercer valor, <m:math><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular cada desviación</strong></p>
            <p>La desviación se calcula como dato menos promedio, es decir, <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Como el promedio es <m:math><m:mn>4,996</m:mn></m:math>, se obtiene:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>4,94</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−0,056</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>4,97</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−0,026</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>4,99</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>5,03</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,034</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>5,05</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4,996</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,054</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Ordenar las desviaciones</strong></p>
            <p>Las desviaciones quedan:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>−0,056</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>−0,026</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>0,034</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>0,054</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>En este caso ya están ordenadas de menor a mayor.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Identificar la mediana</strong></p>
            <p>Como hay cinco datos, la mediana es el valor que queda al centro, es decir, el tercer dato de la lista ordenada.</p>
            <p>El tercer valor es <m:math><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La mediana de las desviaciones es <m:math><m:mn>−0,006</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>